// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1151 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: e219a5e1-9b64-56cd-8352-f7ed11e36a59

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
